{"tid":1892134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"96歲婦初步確診武漢肺炎 曾到北角一間佛堂","createTime":"2020-02-22T10:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:41:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f51759b2f062c216601f288147c02a61d607576","tid":1892134,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sWjxeh6fkltqll5TI40SCQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/d921d940-5545-11ea-bf77-eb337bdacbef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsWjxeh6fkltqll5TI40SCQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2Fd921d940-5545-11ea-bf77-eb337bdacbef&h=35ac2575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續。一名96歲女士今日(22日)初步確診感染新冠肺炎，並留醫東區醫院，她與家人同住，暫時為最高齡確診者，連同此宗個案，香港至今累計70宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，患者居於銅鑼灣天后廟道飛龍臺。她於2月13日晚出現發燒和咳，至今日凌晨情況轉差，出現氣促，其後到東區醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n張指，病人1月底曾到北角一間佛堂，可能為第65宗個案病人所到的佛堂福慧精舍，但仍待確認。96歲病人於2月頭腳痛後沒有出街，目前情況穩定，當局呼籲由初一至今去過該佛堂的市民致電衞生署熱線。"},{"pid":"720132fce1483985bda257b12d6182a5d514aa4f","tid":1892134,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"書局街<br />\n呢度就近福建喇"},{"pid":"16ebffcd4cbe97d6eef7292a03d810950de6ada8","tid":1892134,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"隔左成個月先發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619514a3e5993c4dd8197ce60d47d13362c987d1","tid":1892134,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720132fce1483985bda257b12d6182a5d514aa4f","tid":1892134,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"書局街<br />\n呢度就近福建喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"福慧精舍"}]}